<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idaadc2207-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s7131"><num value="7131">§ 7131.</num><heading> Definition</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this chapter, the term “enlistment” means original enlistment or reenlistment.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idaadc2208-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041">Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70A/177">70A Stat. 177</ref>, § 3251; <ref href="/us/pl/100/180/dA/tXII/s1231/19/A">Pub. L. 100–180, div. A, title XII, § 1231(19)(A)</ref>, <date date="1987-12-04">Dec. 4, 1987</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/101/1161">101 Stat. 1161</ref>; renumbered § 7131, <ref href="/us/pl/115/232/dA/tVIII/s808/b/2">Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII, § 808(b)(2)</ref>, <date date="2018-08-13">Aug. 13, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/1838">132 Stat. 1838</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
